MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: TDSTRBN_COMMENT table hold Distribution comment text details for Cash Reconciliation Manufacturing System in BI Data Mart
MAPPING.NAME: m_SCD_TDSTRBN_COMMENT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Extract records for timestamp>'$$LOAD_LAST_TS'. Initial value of parameter $$LOAD_LAST_TS is '01/01/1111 00:00:00' and is updated with MAX(UPDT_TS) value for each successful run.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DISTINCT DH.DSTR_GID, TV.CORP_CD, MAX(DD.APRV_RECV_TS), DD1.APRV_NOTE_TXT AS DSTRBN_CMT_A_TX, DD2.APRV_NOTE_TXT AS DSTRBN_CMT_M_TX, DD3.APRV_NOTE_TXT AS DSTRBN_CMT_D_TX, DD4.APRV_NOTE_TXT AS DSTRBN_CMT_VP_TX, DD5.APRV_NOTE_TXT AS DSTRBN_CMT_C_TX, DD6.APRV_NOTE_TXT AS DSTRBN_CMT_CM_TX
FROM VRAP.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR DH INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_HDR RH ON DH.RECN_GID=RH.RECN_GID INNER JOIN VRAP.TVNDR TV ON RH.VEND_ID=TV.VNDR_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD.DSTR_GID INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD1 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD1.DSTR_GID AND DD1.APRV_ROLE_CD=1 INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD2 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD2.DSTR_GID AND DD2.APRV_ROLE_CD=2 INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD3 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD3.DSTR_GID AND DD3.APRV_ROLE_CD=3 INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD4 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD4.DSTR_GID AND DD4.APRV_ROLE_CD=4 INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD5 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD5.DSTR_GID AND DD5.APRV_ROLE_CD=5 INNER JOIN VRAP.RCNT_RECN_APRV_DSTR_DTL DD6 ON DH.DSTR_GID=DD6.DSTR_GID AND DD6.APRV_ROLE_CD=6 WHERE DD.APRV_RECV_TS >TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS') GROUP BY DH.DSTR_GID, RH.VEND_ID, TV.CORP_CD, DD1.APRV_NOTE_TXT, DD2.APRV_NOTE_TXT, DD3.APRV_NOTE_TXT, DD4.APRV_NOTE_TXT, DD5.APRV_NOTE_TXT, DD6.APRV_NOTE_TXT WITH UR
